视频。此外，10月19日下午5点，Metal Gear官方合作歌曲《SNEAKING – Song by Mori Calliope》的一部分被公开。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/moricalliope/status/1714551898999558355" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHe6YWzY2AEqvR24ZXy50GpuTxEKPw49y8qqrECnu8q861AT3KqByNBR76Wp9DXQ73QVd6-97bLee0cAk9lw1okvGdbdASZCWELmFZJAWWSTQHsQ-lsDylMoQno1BhXIw2hg17aIewyxnaX5TbrPhhk_=w1097-h1024-s-no-gm" alt=""/></a> </figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/moricalliope/status/1714914280917586430?t=kOA_5ns4G-iwo-yMKuiflg&amp;s=19 </div></figure><p></p><div class="ocmaq6533a40c3101a" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
